Kuwait Lawmaker Asks to Question Information Minister, KUNA Says

-- B y   F i o n a   M a c D o n a l d
-- 
2011-03-29T06:17:15Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-29/kuwait-lawmaker-asks-to-question-information-minister-kuna-says.html
Kuwaiti lawmaker Faisal al-Duwaisan
submitted a request today to question the country’s Information
Minister Sheikh Ahmad al-Abdullah al-Sabah, the state news  KUNA 
reported.  Sheikh Ahmed, who is also  Kuwait ’s oil minister, survived a
no-confidence vote in March last year after parliament
questioned him for allegedly failing to uphold media laws and
protect national unity.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Fiona MacDonald in Kuwait at 
 fmacdonald4@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Shaji Mathew at 
 shajimathew@bloomberg.net  